<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko" class="bg-gray">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>BABATHE.COM - 반품신청</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/library.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/common.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/templateA.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/templateB.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/templateC.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/templateD.css">
    <script src="../../js/swiper-bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../../js/layout.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="sub-hedaer">
            <button type="button" class="btn-back">뒤로가기</button>
            <h1 class="page-title">반품신청</h1>
            <button type="button" class="btn-search">검색</button>
            <button type="button" class="btn-cart">장바구니<span class="num">11</span></button>
        </div>
    </header>
    <section>
        <div class="contentsGroup">
            <div class="infoBar-a bottomLine"><span><strong>ORD20201125140013071</strong> <em>(2020-11-25)</em></span> <a href="#" class="more">더보기</a></div>
            <div class="unitList-orderGoodsInfo shoppingBasket horizontal">
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <div class="thumb ratio-a">
                            <a href="#"><img src="../../img/temp/thumb-168x246.jpg" alt=""></a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="unitInfoWrap">
                            <div class="category">THE IZAAT Collection</div>
                            <div class="title"><a href="#"><strong>밍크 체인 장식 코트형 트워드 베스트</strong></a></div>
                            <div class="goodsOptions">Black / 55</div>
                            <div class="goodsOptions">수량: 1개</div>
                            <div class="bottomWrap">
                                <div class="priceWrap">
                                    <div class="price">1,296.743원</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="optionWrap">
                            <strong>반품수량</strong>
                            <div class="countUi disabled">
                                <button class="btn-minus">-</button>
                                <input type="tel" value="3">
                                <button class="btn-plus">+</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="optionWrap total">
                            <strong>반품금액</strong>
                            <span>2,154,600원</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="optionWrap vertical">
                            <div class="selectWrap">
                                <select class="placeholderOn" disabled>
                                    <option selected disabled hidden>단순변심</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                            <textarea cols="30" rows="5" readonly>그냥 반품요</textarea>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="contentsGroup">
            <h2>수거지 정보</h2>
            <div class="list-info fixLeft">
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <strong>수거지 정보</strong>
                        <span>김바바(집)<br>010-0000-0000<br>서울특별시 서초구 신반포로 339, 논현빌딩</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="vertical">
                        <strong>수거메시지</strong>
                        <span>
                            <select disabled>
                                <option>경비실에 맡겨 놓겠습니다.</option>
                            </select>
                        </span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="contentsGroup">
            <h2>결제 정보</h2>
            <div class="list-info">
                <ul>
                    <li class="total">
                        <strong>최종 결제금액</strong>
                        <span>1,761,323원</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="contentsGroup">
            <h2>결제 수단</h2>
            <div class="list-info">
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <strong>가상계좌입금</strong>
                        <span>9,240,780원</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>계좌번호</strong>
                        <span>기업은행 12-4566-456-44</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>입금일</strong>
                        <span>2020-03-21</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="contentsGroup">
            <div class="txtInfoBox-e">반품배송비 5,000원</div>
            <h2>배송비 쿠폰</h2>
            <li class="form-flex priceAndPoint">
                <div class="form-flex-cell">
                    <input type="text" disabled>
                    <span class="unit">원</span>
                </div>

                <div class="form-flex-btn">
                    <button class="btn-basicM" disabled>쿠폰사용</button>
                </div>
            </li>
        </div>
        <div class="contentsGroup">
            <h2>환불정보</h2>
            <div class="list-info">
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <strong>반품상품 결제금액</strong>
                        <span>1,761,323원</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>반품배송비</strong>
                        <span>-2,500원</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>배송비 쿠폰</strong>
                        <span>2,500원</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="total lineBold">
                        <strong>환불(예정) 금액</strong>
                        <span class="pink">922,323원</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="alertTxt">환불금액이 차감금액보다 부족하여 추가 결제가 필요합니다.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="contentsGroup">
            <h2>결제수단 선택</h2>
            <div class="select-payment">
                <div class="inner">
                    <label>
                        <input type="radio" name="selectPayment" checked>
                        <div class="item">
                            <span>
                                <strong>신용카드</strong>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </label>
                    <label>
                        <input type="radio" name="selectPayment">
                        <div class="item">
                            <span>
                                <strong>실시간 계좌이체</strong>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </label>
                    <label>
                        <input type="radio" name="selectPayment">
                        <div class="item">
                            <span>
                                <strong>네이버페이</strong>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </label>
                    <label>
                        <input type="radio" name="selectPayment">
                        <div class="item">
                            <span>
                                <strong>카카오페이</strong>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </label>
                    <label>
                        <input type="radio" name="selectPayment">
                        <div class="item">
                            <span>
                                <strong>삼성페이</strong>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </label>
                    <label>
                        <input type="radio" name="selectPayment">
                        <div class="item">
                            <span>
                                <strong>페이코</strong>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </label>
                    <label>
                        <input type="radio" name="selectPayment">
                        <div class="item">
                            <span>
                                <strong>토스</strong>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </label>
                    <label>
                        <input type="radio" name="selectPayment">
                        <div class="item">
                            <span>
                                <strong>스마일페이</strong>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="selectWrap">
                <select class="placeholderOn">
                    <option selected disabled hidden>카드 선택</option>
                    <option>카드1</option>
                    <option>카드2</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <div class="chkWrap">
                <label><input type="checkbox" class="type2"><span>지금 선택한 결제수단을 다음에도 사용</span></label>
            </div>
            <ul class="tip-wrap">
                <li class="tip type3">[반품신청 확인]을 누르시면 추가 결제와 동시에 반품신청이 완료됩니다.</li>
                <li class="tip type3">주문 시 사용하셨던 쿠폰 및 포인트는 사용 이전으로 원복됩니다.</li>
                <li class="tip type3">환불금액은 반품 확정 후 결정되므로, 환불예정금액과 상이할 수 있습니다.</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="btnWrap">
                <button class="btn-basicM">이전</button>
                <button class="btn-basicM blackSolid">반품신청 확인</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <footer></footer>
</body>
</html>